{
  "texts": [
    "Chen et al. (2024c) utilized LLM to support conceptual design using a specific design approach, morphological analysis.",
    "Their findings showed that integrating LLM into the design process could enhance innovation, functionality, and, ultimately, the quality of design ideas, which aligns with the results of our experiments.",
    "In their 2024 study, Jiang and Luo introduced Auto-TRIZ, a design model that uses LLM to automate TRIZ.",
    "The model takes problem statements from users as initial inputs and directly generates a solution report by following the TRIZ process.",
    "One feature of this model is the automatic generation of contradictions by machines, which occurs without the need for designer supervision."
  ]
}